80945>>>        Procedure AddDDs integer hDD
80948>>>            Integer iCnt
80948>>>            String sName
80948>>>            Get Combo_Item_Count to iCnt
80949>>>            Get Object_label of hDD to sName
80950>>>            Send Combo_Add_Item sName
80951>>>            Set Aux_Value of (combo_data_object(self)) iCnt to hDD
