80956>>>        Procedure Fill_List
80959>>>            Integer hVw
80959>>>            Get phoInvokingView to hVw
80960>>>            Send Combo_Delete_Data
80961>>>            Broadcast Send EnumerateDDs to hVw msg_AddDDs Self
80963>>>            //Set Value 0 to (Combo_value(self,0))
80963>>>            Send onChange
80964>>>        End_Procedure
80965>>>
