82052>>>    Procedure RefreshAll
82055>>>        Integer hDD
82055>>>        Boolean bIsRecnumTable
82055>>>        get phoCurrentDD to hDD
82056>>>        Get IsRecnumTable (main_file(hDD)) to bIsRecnumTable
82057>>>        Set Value          of oCurRec 0 to (If(bIsRecnumTable, current_record(hDD), 0))
82058>>>        Set checked_state  of oChangedState to (Changed_State(hDD))
82059>>>        set checked_state  of oShouldSave   to (Should_save(hDD))
82060>>>        Send RefreshAll    of (phoFieldsEditId(self))
82061>>>        Send RefreshCounts of oFindCounts
82062>>>    End_procedure
