82397>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82397>>>>>>>//*** Class  : cDfbtrdrvHandler                                                  ***
82397>>>>>>>//*** Purpose: An instance of this class can be used as a broker object to  ***
82397>>>>>>>//***          call several Dfbtrdrv releated methods.                           ***
