82461>>>>>>>    Function CKMinorRevision Returns Integer
82463>>>>>>>        Function_Return (ExtractPartFromRevision (Current_Object, 2, CKRevision(Current_Object)))
82464>>>>>>>    End_Function // CKMinorRevision
82465>>>>>>>
82465>>>>>>>
82465>>>>>>>
82465>>>>>>>    //***
