82465>>>>>>>    Function CKReleaseRevision Returns Integer
82467>>>>>>>        Function_Return (ExtractPartFromRevision (Current_Object, 3, CKRevision(Current_Object)))
82468>>>>>>>    End_Function // CKReleaseRevision
82469>>>>>>>
82469>>>>>>>
