82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>//*** DB2_DRV.PKG                                                           ***
82763>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82763>>>>>>>//*** Author: Ben Weijers                                                   ***
82763>>>>>>>//***         Data Access Nederland                                         ***
82763>>>>>>>//***         30 July 1998                                                  ***
82763>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82763>>>>>>>//*** Last updated: May 2, 2007                                                                      ***
82763>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82763>>>>>>>//*** Purpose:                                                              ***
82763>>>>>>>//***   Package that declares DB2 driver constants and functions.           ***
82763>>>>>>>//****                                                                      ***
82763>>>>>>>//***   This package can be used by developers who want to add DB2 driver   ***
82763>>>>>>>//***   specific code to a DataFlex application.                            ***
82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>Use Cli.pkg
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*** Driver attributes
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*** Driver Indentification
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*** Error number constants
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*** Call driver function identifiers
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>// DB2 specific data types
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_CLOB           for   (-99)  
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_BLOB           for   (-98)  
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_XML            for   (-370) 
82763>>>>>>>// DB2 Graphic types are Unicode types
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_GRAPHIC        for   (-95)  
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_VARGRAPHIC     for   (-96)  
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_LONGVARGRAPHIC for   (-97)  
82763>>>>>>>Define SQL_DBCLOB         for   (-350) 
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*** Extra DB2 commands
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>//*** DB2_CheckTrigger <NewState>                                           ***
82763>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82763>>>>>>>//*** This command will set the trigger check at open on or off.            ***
82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>//*** DB2_SetConstraint <FileNum> <ConstraintText>                          ***
82763>>>>>>>//***                                                                       ***
82763>>>>>>>//***   Setup a constraint for a file.                                      ***
82763>>>>>>>//*****************************************************************************
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>
82763>>>>>>>Class cDB2Handler Is A cCLIHandler
82764>>>>>>>
82764>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
82766>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
82768>>>>>>>
82768>>>>>>>        Set psDriverID To DB2_DRV_ID
