83018>>>>>>>/// corresponding to the specified file number. In a restructure operation
83018>>>>>>>/// this attribute may be used to permanently change the table that a filelist
83018>>>>>>>/// entry is pointing to.
83018>>>>>>>///
83018>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions
83018>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
83018>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     All
83018>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-07-15 by Oliver Nelson
83018>>>>>>>/// @See
83018>>>>>>>/// @INTOPT DATABASE_NAME {string}
83018>>>>>>>///
83018>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Get_Attribute DF_FILE_TABLE_NAME of {FileNumber} to {variable}
83018>>>>>>>/// @Syntax Set_Attribute DF_FILE_TABLE_NAME of {FileNumber} to {variable}
