83018>>>>>>>/// In DataFlex, this is usually done with the REREAD/UNLOCK commands. This
83018>>>>>>>/// attribute is used to get the status of a table lock. If a table is currently
83018>>>>>>>/// in a REREAD, or locked, then the attribute will return true. Otherwise, it
83018>>>>>>>/// returns false. It is a read-only attribute so no setting can be done.
83018>>>>>>>///
83018>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions
83018>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
