84023>>>>>>>/// @Status      Deprecated
84023>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     SQLFlex
84023>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-10-01 by Aaron Gulack
84023>>>>>>>/// @See                 GET_DRIVER_REVISION
84023>>>>>>>///
84023>>>>>>>/// @Syntax SQLFlex_REVISION {variable}
84023>>>>>>>/// @Param variable                     String variable to hold the returned version
84023>>>>>>>///
84023>>>>>>>/// @Example
84023>>>>>>>/// SQLFlex_REVISION sVersion
84023>>>>>>>
84023>>>>>>>//=============================================================================
84023>>>>>>>/// @Name        SQLFlex_MAJOR_REVISION
84023>>>>>>>/// @Description This command will put the major version (no decimals) of
84023>>>>>>>/// the the MSSQL driver associated with the current workspace into the
