84067>>>>>>>/// @Name        SET_MIRROR_SERVER
84067>>>>>>>/// @Description This command is used to programmatically set the mirror
84067>>>>>>>/// server for the database. This is to be used along with SQl server
84067>>>>>>>/// failover mirroring. Note that this simply sets the server and database
84067>>>>>>>/// to be used for mirroring. All set up for the servers must already be
84067>>>>>>>/// working properly through SQL Server.
84067>>>>>>>///
84067>>>>>>>/// @Assumptions A compatible version of SQL Server is being used
84067>>>>>>>/// @Status      Public
84067>>>>>>>/// @Drivers     SQLFlex v9.2 and above
84067>>>>>>>/// @VersionNote Last Revised: 2013-10-02 by Aaron Gulack
