84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwMemoryLoad     as DWord // percent Of memory in use
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalPhys      as DWord // bytes Of physical memory
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailPhys      as DWord // free physical memory bytes
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalPageFile  as DWord // bytes Of paging file
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailPageFile  as DWord // free bytes Of paging file
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwTotalVirtual   as DWord // user bytes Of address space
84318>>>>>   Field MEMORYSTATUS.dwAvailVirtual   as DWord // free user bytes
84318>>>>>End_Type
