84460>>>>>        Case Begin
84460>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_USA)
84462>>>>>                Move C_$USA To sDateFormat
84463>>>>>                Case Break
84464>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_EUROPEAN)
84467>>>>>                Move C_$European To sDateFormat
84468>>>>>                Case Break
84469>>>>>            Case (iDateFormat = DF_DATE_MILITARY)
84472>>>>>                Move C_$Military To sDateFormat
84473>>>>>                Case Break
84474>>>>>            Case Else
84474>>>>>                Move C_$UnknownDateType To sDateFormat
84475>>>>>                Case Break
84476>>>>>        Case End
84476>>>>>
84476>>>>>        Send AppendTextLn (SFormat (C_$DateFormat, sDateformat))
84477>>>>>    End_Procedure
