85481>>>>>    
85481>>>>>    // do a search using the current keys in the search key buffer for the sort column.
85481>>>>>    // Becaue this is called via an OnIdle it is possible to have multiple keys pressed before
85481>>>>>    // the OnIdle. These have been stored in pSearchKeys and will be passed to the popup dialog
85481>>>>>    Procedure Request_SearchEx
85483>>>>>        tGridKeyPair[] Keys
85483>>>>>        tGridKeyPair[] Keys
85484>>>>>        Integer iCol
85484>>>>>        Handle hoCol hoSearchDialog 
85484>>>>>        Boolean bOk
85484>>>>>        String sValue
85484>>>>>
85484>>>>>        Get piSortColumn to iCol
85485>>>>>        If (iCol<>-1) Begin
85487>>>>>            Get ColumnObject iCol to hoCol
85488>>>>>                Get pSearchKeys to Keys
85489>>>>>            Get CreateGridSearchDialogObject to hoSearchDialog
85490>>>>>            Get RequestGridSearchEx of hoSearchDialog Keys hoCol (&sValue) to bOk
85491>>>>>            If bOk Begin
85493>>>>>               Send RequestFindColumnValue iCol sValue True 0  
85494>>>>>            End
85494>>>>>>
85494>>>>>            Send Destroy of hoSearchDialog
85495>>>>>        End
85495>>>>>>
85495>>>>>        Send ClearSearchRequest // clear the search keys
85496>>>>>    End_Procedure
