85514>>>>>//****************************************************************************
85514>>>>>// $Module type: Class
85514>>>>>// $Module name: cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary
85514>>>>>// $Author     : Nils G. Svedmyr, RDC Tools International, <mailto:support@rdctools.com>
85514>>>>>// Web-site    : http://www.rdctools.com
85514>>>>>// Created     : 2014-09-05 @ 09:50 (Military date format: YY-MM-DD)
85514>>>>>//
85514>>>>>// Description : The class consists of a function library for database manipulations, aka make changes to a database.
85514>>>>>//               It has top level functions that uses the DataFlex db API, _but_ also specialized
85514>>>>>//               functions to make db changes to Sql databases with the DAW & Mertech drivers,
85514>>>>>//               with the help of Sql-scripts.
85514>>>>>//
85514>>>>>// $Rev History:
85514>>>>>//    2014-09-05  Module header created
85514>>>>>//   
85514>>>>>//****************************************************************************
