85646>>>>>>>>>            Set Window_Style To PBS_VERTICAL (private_pbVertical(self))
85647>>>>>>>>>            Set Window_Style To PBS_SMOOTH   (private_pbSmooth(self))
85648>>>>>>>>>            Forward Send Page_Object True
85650>>>>>>>>>        End
85650>>>>>>>>>>
