85837>>>>>>>// *** Mixin Class For the cDbUpdateFunctionLibrary Class ***                          
85837>>>>>>>//
85837>>>>>>>// We need to create a mixin class for the library.
85837>>>>>>>// Why? Because we import the library to the cDbUpdateVersion class; that imports
85837>>>>>>>// all messages (functions & procedures) but all Properties are "lost", aka not imported by
85837>>>>>>>// the Import_Class_Protocol command. So we need a way to create our properties somewhere else...
85837>>>>>>>// Note: This class should _not_ have a construct_object defined.
85837>>>>>>>//
