86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// The ShellExecute function opens or prints a specified file. The file can be an
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// executable file or a document file.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Operation can be one of the following:
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//    "OPEN"  The function opens the file specified by lpFile.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file can be an executable file or a document file.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file can be a folder to open.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//    "PRINT" The function prints the file specified by lpFile.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            The file should be a document file. If the file is an executable file,
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//            the function opens the file, as if "open" had been specified.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//  "EXPLORE" The function explores the folder specified by lpFile.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Return Values:
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// If the function succeeds, the return value is the instance handle of the application that
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// was run, or the handle of a dynamic data exchange (DDE) server application.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// If the function fails, the return value is an error value that is less than or equal to 32.
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>//
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// The following table lists these error values:
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_FILE_NOT_FOUND = 2&
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_PATH_NOT_FOUND = 3&
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const ERROR_BAD_FORMAT = 11&
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_ACCESSDENIED = 5
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_ASSOCINCOMPLETE = 27
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDEBUSY = 30
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDEFAIL = 29
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DDETIMEOUT = 28
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_DLLNOTFOUND = 32
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_FNF = 2
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_NOASSOC = 31
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_OOM = 8
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_PNF = 3
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>// Public Const SE_ERR_SHARE = 26
86118>>>>>>>>>>>>>
