86132>>>>>>>>>>>>>// incorrectly into an unsigned integer.
86132>>>>>>>>>>>>>// I don't have the time to dive into this.. so added a workaround (and removed it again)
86132>>>>>>>>>>>>>// It does smell a bit fishy though
