86437>>>>>>>>>>>    Get FileOperation sFileName "" vFO_DELETE iFlags To iRetVal
86438>>>>>>>>>>>    Function_Return iRetVal
86439>>>>>>>>>>>  End_Function // sfoDeleteFile
