86497>>>>>>>>>>>// Restore to the old way of working with the shell file operations.
86497>>>>>>>>>>>// or.. to put lay man terms, allow any of the operations vDeleteFile
86497>>>>>>>>>>>// vCopyFile/vMoveFile/vRenameFile to have an UNDO
86497>>>>>>>>>>>Procedure vWin32fhCompatibilityMode
86500>>>>>>>>>>>  Integer hoSFO
86500>>>>>>>>>>>  Integer iFlags
86500>>>>>>>>>>>  
86500>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (vFOF_SILENT Ior vFOF_NOCONFIRMATION Ior vFOF_ALLOWUNDO) To iFlags
86501>>>>>>>>>>>  Move (oShellFileOperations(Self)) To hoSFO
86502>>>>>>>>>>>  
86502>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piDeleteFlags Of hoSFO To iFlags
86503>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piCopyFlags   Of hoSFO To iFlags
86504>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piMoveFlags   Of hoSFO To iFlags
86505>>>>>>>>>>>  Set piRenameFlags Of hoSFO To iFlags
86506>>>>>>>>>>>End_Procedure // vWin32fhCompatibilityMode
