88146>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLSetNextArgument String sArgument
88148>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iArgnum
88148>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88148>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get piLastArgument to iArgnum
88149>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Increment iArgnum
88150>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Send SQLSetArgument iArgnum sArgument
88151>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set piLastArgument to iArgnum
88152>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLSetNextArgument
88153>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88153>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLSetArgument Integer iArgnum String sArgument
88155>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParams
88156>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88156>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get pvParams to vParams
88157>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sArgument to vParams[iArgnum-1]
88158>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set pvParams to vParams
88159>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88159>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLSetArgument
88160>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88160>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLCall
88162>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParams
88163>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Variant[] vParamOpts
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer i
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iMax
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iParamsIn 
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sParameter
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bIsProcedure
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88164>>>>>>>>>>>>>        SQL_SET_CURRENT_CURSOR_STMT to (piCursorNum(Self))
88178>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88178>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88178>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get pvParams to vParams
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // First, we need to figure out if this is a procedure or a function. Then if
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // it's a procedure, "analyze" it to figure out which parameters are IN, 
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // OUT, or IN_OUT.  Then we adjust how we call SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        // so that after the call you can retrieve the value.
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88179>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get IsProcedure (psProcName(Self)) to bIsProcedure
88180>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88180>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (bIsProcedure) Begin
88182>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get ProcParams (psProcName(Self)) to vParamOpts
88183>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88183>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (sizeOfArray(vParamOpts)) to iMax
88184>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (SizeOfArray(vParams)) to iParamsIn
88185>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set piParameterCount to iMax
88186>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88186>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_NAME (psProcName(Self)) NUMPAR iMax 
88206>>>>>>>>>>>>>            For i from 1 to iMax
88212>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88212>>>>>>>>>>>>>                If ( (i-1) >= iParamsIn) Move "" to sParameter
88215>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Else Move vParams[i-1] to sParameter
88217>>>>>>>>>>>>>                
88217>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Begin
88217>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "IN")
88219>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter IN
88260>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88260>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break
88261>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "OUT")
88264>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter OUT
88305>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88305>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break
88306>>>>>>>>>>>>>                    Case (vParamOpts[i-1] = "IN/OUT" or vParamOpts[i-1] = "INOUT")
88309>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        SQL_SET_PROCEDURE_PARAMETER i to sParameter IN_OUT
88350>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88350>>>>>>>>>>>>>                        Case Break     
88351>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Case End
88351>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Loop
88352>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88352>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88352>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_PROCEDURE_EXECUTE
88367>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88367>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88367>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Begin
88368>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_SET_FUNCTION_NAME (psProcName(Self)) NUMPAR (SizeOfArray(vParams))
88392>>>>>>>>>>>>>            For i from 1 to (SizeOfArray(vParams))
88398>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88398>>>>>>>>>>>>>                SQL_SET_FUNCTION_PARAMETER i to vParams[i-1]
88470>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88470>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Loop
88471>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88471>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88471>>>>>>>>>>>>>            SQL_FUNCTION_EXECUTE
88472>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88472>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88472>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
88473>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88473>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLGetNextArgument Returns String
88475>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Local Integer iArgnum
88475>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Local String  sResult
88475>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88475>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get piLastArgument to iArgnum
88476>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Increment iArgnum
88477>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get SQLGetArgument iArgnum to sResult
88478>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set piLastArgument to iArgnum
88479>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88479>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sResult
88480>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // SQLGetNextArgument
