88612>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLConnect String sDriver String sConnect Returns Handle
88614>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88614>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88615>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88615>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88615>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88615>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88616>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sDriver to conn.sDriver
88617>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move sConnect to conn.sConnect
88618>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88618>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (SizeOfArray(maps) > 0) Move (maps[(SizeOfArray(maps)-1)].iHdbc+1) to conn.iHdbc
88621>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Move 1 to conn.iHdbc
88623>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88623>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Set CurrentConnection to sDriver sConnect 
88624>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Err)) Begin
88626>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move conn to maps[(SizeOfArray(maps))]
88627>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88628>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set ptCLIHandleMap to conn
88629>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88629>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88629>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88629>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return Self
88630>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88631>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88631>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLFileConnect Integer iFileNum Returns Integer
88633>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bIsOpen
88633>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriver sServer
88633>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88633>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88634>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88634>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap conn
88634>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88634>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_FILE_OPENED of iFileNum to bIsOpen
88637>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (bIsOpen) Begin
88639>>>>>>>>>>>>>            //*** Fill the driver id, assume longest is 255 characters
88639>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(' ', 255)) to sDriver
88640>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Repeat(' ', 255)) to sServer
88641>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FILE_DRIVER of iFileNum to sDriver
88644>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_FILE_SERVER_NAME of iFileNum to sServer
88647>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88647>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Indicate Err False
88648>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88648>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88649>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move sDriver to conn.sDriver
88650>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move sServer to conn.sConnect
88651>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88651>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (SizeOfArray(maps) > 0) Move (maps[(SizeOfArray(maps)-1)].iHdbc+1) to conn.iHdbc
88654>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Move 1 to conn.iHdbc
88656>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88656>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set CurrentConnection to sDriver sServer 
88657>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (not(Err)) Begin
88659>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Move conn to maps[(SizeOfArray(maps))]
88660>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Set ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88661>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Set ptCLIHandleMap to conn
88662>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88662>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88662>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88662>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send StoreHandleInfo conn.iHdbc conn.sDriver
88663>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set piBindFile to iFileNum
88664>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88664>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88664>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Error 4099 "File Not Open"
88666>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88666>>>>>>>>>>>>>        //*** Return success status
88666>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return (not(Err))
88667>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88668>>>>>>>>>>>>>    
88668>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure SQLDisconnect
88670>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap map
