88670>>>>>>>>>>>>>        tCLIHandleMap[] maps
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iFound
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88671>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMap to map
88672>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get ptCLIHandleMaps to maps
88673>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88673>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Move (SearchArray(map, maps, Parent(Self), RefFunc(CompareMaps))) to iFound
88674>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (iFound > -1) Begin
88676>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle
88677>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88677>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88677>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure // SQLDisconnect
