88705>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function DriverIndex String sDriver Returns Integer
88707>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sCurrentDriver
88707>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iDriver
88707>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iNumDrivers
88707>>>>>>>>>>>>>     
88707>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get_Attribute DF_NUMBER_DRIVERS to iNumDrivers
88710>>>>>>>>>>>>>        For iDriver from 1 to iNumDrivers
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88716>>>>>>>>>>>>>          Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_NAME of iDriver to sCurrentDriver
88719>>>>>>>>>>>>>          If (Uppercase(sDriver) = Uppercase(sCurrentDriver)) ;              Function_Return iDriver
88722>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Loop
88723>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88723>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return 0
88724>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // DriverIndex
88725>>>>>>>>>>>>> 
88725>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function FirstServerForDriverNo Integer iDriver Returns String 
88727>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sServer
88727>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iNumServers
88727>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iServer 
88727>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88727>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (iDriver <> 0) Begin
88729>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_NUMBER_SERVERS of iDriver to iNumServers
88732>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (iNumServers<>0) Begin
88734>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Move 1 to iServer
88735>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Get_Attribute DF_DRIVER_SERVER_NAME of iDriver iServer to sServer
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End 
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88738>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sServer
88739>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
88740>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88740>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Set CurrentConnection String sDriver String sServer
88742>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Integer iDriver 
88742>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sUsername 
88742>>>>>>>>>>>>>        String sPassword 
88742>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88742>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (sDriver="") Begin 
88744>>>>>>>>>>>>>            DO_GETFILENUMBER_DRIVERNAME 0
88746>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move MertechInc_DriverName to sDriver
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88747>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If ("MDSMYSQL|ORA_DRV|MDSPGSQL|SQL_DRV|MDS_DB2" contains Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) Begin
88749>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move (Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) to MertechInc_DriverName
88750>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88750>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (Trim(sDriver) <> "") Move (Uppercase(Trim(sDriver))) to MertechInc_CurrentDriver
88753>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Move "" to MertechInc_CurrentDriver
88755>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88755>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get psUsername to sUsername
88756>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get psPassword to sPassword 
88757>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88757>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Get DriverIndex MertechInc_CurrentDriver to iDriver
88758>>>>>>>>>>>>>            
88758>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sServer="") Get FirstServerForDriverNo iDriver to sServer
88761>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sUsername="") GET_CURRENT_USER_NAME of sServer to sUsername
88778>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (sPassword="") get_current_user_password of sServer to sPassword
88795>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Move False to Err  
88796>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id 25000
88797>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Login sServer sUsername sPassword sDriver
88799>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id 25000
88800>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If (Err = False) Begin
88802>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Call_Driver 0 MertechInc_DriverName Function CALLDRV_CURRENT_SQL_SERVER_CONNECTION CALLBACK 0 PASSING sServer MertechInc_Blank 0 RESULT MertechInc_iRet
88807>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88807>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88807>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Else Begin
88808>>>>>>>>>>>>>                Procedure_Return
88809>>>>>>>>>>>>>            End
88809>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88809>>>>>>>>>>>>>                
88809>>>>>>>>>>>>>            If MertechInc_iRet EQ -1 INDICATE ERR True
88812>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88812>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88812>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Else Error 4099 "Invalid Driver"
88814>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88814>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
88815>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88815>>>>>>>>>>>>>End_Class
