88841>>>>>>>>>>>>>    Function SQLConnect String sDriver String sConnect String sUsername String sPassword Returns Handle
88843>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hSql
88843>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bOK
88843>>>>>>>>>>>>>  
88843>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get CreateHandle to hSql
88844>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
