88850>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set psUsername of hSql to sUsername
88851>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Set psPassword of hSql to sPassword
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88852>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Get SQLConnect of hSql sDriver sConnect to bOK
88853>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(bOK)) Begin
88855>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle of hSQL
88856>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return 0
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        
88857>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hSql
88858>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
