88863>>>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(bOK)) Begin
88865>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Send FreeHandle of hSql
88866>>>>>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return 0
88867>>>>>>>>>>>>>        End
88867>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88867>>>>>>>>>>>>>
88867>>>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return hSql
88868>>>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function // SQLFileConnect
