89183>>>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDB2Driver is a cDbUpdateGenericDatabaseDriver
89184>>>>>>>>>>>    Function DbLogin String sConnectionString String sServer String sDatabase Boolean bTrusted String sUserID String sPassword Returns Boolean
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        Boolean bLoginSuccessful
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID 
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        
89186>>>>>>>>>>>        Move False to Err
89187>>>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
89188>>>>>>>>>>>        If (not(Uppercase(sServer) contains "DSN")) Begin
89190>>>>>>>>>>>            Move ("DSN=" + sServer) to sServer
89191>>>>>>>>>>>        End
89191>>>>>>>>>>>>
89191>>>>>>>>>>>        Login sServer sUserId sPassword sDriverID
89193>>>>>>>>>>>        
89193>>>>>>>>>>>        Move (not(Err)) to bLoginSuccessful
89194>>>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return bLoginSuccessful
89195>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Function
89196>>>>>>>>>>>End_Class
