89268>>>>>>>>>>>Class cDbUpdateDatabaseDriver is a cObject
89269>>>>>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
89271>>>>>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
89273>>>>>>>>>>>        Property String psDriverID DATAFLEX_ID
89274>>>>>>>>>>>        Property Handle phoDriverSpecificObject
89275>>>>>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
89276>>>>>>>>>>>    
89276>>>>>>>>>>>    Function CreateDriver Returns Handle
89278>>>>>>>>>>>        String sDriverID
89278>>>>>>>>>>>        Handle hoDriver hcDriverClass
89278>>>>>>>>>>>        
89278>>>>>>>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
89279>>>>>>>>>>>        Case Begin
89279>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)
89281>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMSSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89282>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89283>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ODBC_DRV_ID)
89286>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateODBCDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89287>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89288>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID)
89291>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDB2Driver)) to hcDriverClass
89292>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89293>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = SQLFLEX)
89296>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateSQLFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89297>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89298>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX)
89301>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateORAFLEXDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89302>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89303>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL)
89306>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSPgSQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89307>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89308>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL)
89311>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateMDSMySQLDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89312>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89313>>>>>>>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DATAFLEX_ID)
89316>>>>>>>>>>>                Move (RefClass(cDbUpdateDataFlexDriver)) to hcDriverClass
89317>>>>>>>>>>>                Case Break
89318>>>>>>>>>>>            Case Else
89318>>>>>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
89319>>>>>>>>>>>        Case End
89319>>>>>>>>>>>        
89319>>>>>>>>>>>        Get Create hcDriverClass to hoDriver
89320>>>>>>>>>>>        Set psDriverID of hoDriver to sDriverID
89321>>>>>>>>>>>        Set phoDriverSpecificObject to hoDriver
