89392>>>>>>>>>        Get psIniFileName to sIniFile
89393>>>>>>>>>        Move (sPath + sIniFile) to sIniFile
89394>>>>>>>>>        Set psFileName to sIniFile
89395>>>>>>>>>        Get ReadString sSection sValueName sDefaultValue to sValue
89396>>>>>>>>>
89396>>>>>>>>>        Function_Return sValue
89397>>>>>>>>>    End_Function                     
