89417>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return (GT) 
89418>>>>>>>>>        End
89418>>>>>>>>>>
89418>>>>>>>>>
89418>>>>>>>>>        If (SQLConnectionRow1.sServer < SQLConnectionRow2.sServer) Begin
89420>>>>>>>>>            Function_Return (LT)
89421>>>>>>>>>        End
89421>>>>>>>>>>
