90047>>>>>>>            Move MSSQLDRV_ID to SQLConnection.sDriverID // Default is the MS-SQL driver.
90048>>>>>>>        End
90048>>>>>>>>
90048>>>>>>>        Function_Return SQLConnection.sDriverID
90049>>>>>>>    End_Function  
