90818>>>>>>>    // Sample sConnString: "SERVER=(local)\SQLEXPRESS;UID=dbuser;PWD=secret;DATABASE=OrderEntry;, 0"
90818>>>>>>>    // Pass a complete driver connection string
90818>>>>>>>    // Returns the following as a struct:
90818>>>>>>>    //   sServer, sDatabase, sUser, sPassword & True if Trusted_Connection is used.
90818>>>>>>>    // Finally also returns a boolean TRUE if trusted_connection=yes, else false is returned. 
