91136>>>>>    // *** Sql View Messages ***
91136>>>>>
91136>>>>>    // First deletes the data cache file and then drops the passed Sql data view. 
91136>>>>>    Function SqlViewRemove String sDataView Returns Boolean
91138>>>>>        String sDriverID sSQLString sPath sDropViewKeyWord 
91138>>>>>        Integer iRetval                                
91138>>>>>        Boolean bMertechDriver bOK
91138>>>>>        
91138>>>>>        Get psDriverID to sDriverID
