91140>>>>>        Get UtilDeleteCacheFile sDataView to iRetval
91141>>>>>        
91141>>>>>        Get _SqlFindKeyWord CI_SQLDropView to sDropViewKeyWord
91142>>>>>        Move (sDropViewKeyWord * String(sDataView)) to sSQLString
91143>>>>>        Set psSQLStatementString to sSQLString 
91144>>>>>        
91144>>>>>        // As we don't check if the view exist or not, it might happen
91144>>>>>        // that it doesn't and that would through an error, so guard for that eventuality (just ignore it).
91144>>>>>        Move False to Err 
