91923>>>>>    // Checks if a table exists as an SQL table. Returns = True if it does.
91923>>>>>    Function SqlUtilCheckIfTableNameExists String sTableName String sDriverID Returns Boolean
91925>>>>>        String sVal
91925>>>>>        Boolean bExists  
91925>>>>>        String[] sTablesArray                                 
91926>>>>>        Integer iSize iCount
91926>>>>>        
91926>>>>>        Move False to bExists
91927>>>>>        Get SqlUtilEnumerateTables sDriverID to sTablesArray  
91928>>>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(sTablesArray)) to iSize
91929>>>>>        Decrement iSize
91930>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
91936>>>>>>
91936>>>>>            Move sTablesArray[iCount] to sVal
91937>>>>>            If (Uppercase(sVal) = Uppercase(sTableName)) Begin
91939>>>>>                Move True to bExists
91940>>>>>                Move iSize to iCount // We're done!
91941>>>>>            End
91941>>>>>>
91941>>>>>        Loop
91942>>>>>>
91942>>>>>    
91942>>>>>        Function_Return bExists
91943>>>>>    End_Function   
