92062>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX)  
92065>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech "SELECT NAME FROM v$database" to sReturnArray
92066>>>>>                Case Break
92067>>>>>
92067>>>>>            Case Else
92067>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM "Unsupported DriverID passed to SqlUtilEnumerateDatabases function"
92068>>>>>>
92068>>>>>        Case End  
92068>>>>>        
92068>>>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
92069>>>>>    End_Function
