92196>>>>>        End   
92196>>>>>>
92196>>>>>       
92196>>>>>        Get psConnectionString to sConnectionString  
92197>>>>>        Get psSchema to sSchema
92198>>>>>        
92198>>>>>        Case Begin
92198>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)    
92200>>>>>                Move ("select name from sys.columns where [object_id] = object_id('dbo." + sTableName + "')") to sSelect
92201>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlDAW sSelect 1 to sReturnArray
92202>>>>>                Case Break
92203>>>>>
92203>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = DB2_DRV_ID) 
