92213>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 1 to sReturnArray
92214>>>>>                Case Break
92215>>>>>            
92215>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSMySQL) 
92218>>>>>                Move ("SHOW COLUMNS FROM" * sTableName) to sSelect
92219>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 1 to sReturnArray
92220>>>>>                Case Break
92221>>>>>            
92221>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MDSPgSQL) 
92224>>>>>                Move ("select column_name, data_type, character_maximum_length from INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS where table_name = '" +sTableName + "'") to sSelect
92225>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 1 to sReturnArray
92226>>>>>                Case Break            
92227>>>>>            
92227>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = ORAFLEX) 
92230>>>>>                Move ("SELECT column_name from user_tab_cols WHERE table_name = '" + sTableName + "'") to sSelect
92231>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 1 to sReturnArray
92232>>>>>                Case Break
92233>>>>>                            
92233>>>>>            Case Else     
92233>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM "Unsupported driver passed to SqlUtilEnumerateColumns function."
92234>>>>>>
92234>>>>>                Case Break
92235>>>>>        Case End
92235>>>>>        
92235>>>>>        Function_Return sReturnArray
92236>>>>>    End_Function  
