92338>>>>>>
92338>>>>>                Case Break
92339>>>>>        Case End   
92339>>>>>        
92339>>>>>        Move (Length(sTableName)) to iLength
92340>>>>>        Move (iLength + 4)        to iLength // The related to field key has the format "FK_TableName + FieldName"
92341>>>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(sFileNameArray)) to iSize
92342>>>>>        Decrement iSize
92343>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
92349>>>>>>
92349>>>>>            If (Trim(sFileNameArray[iCount]) <> "") Begin
92351>>>>>                Move sFileNameArray[iCount]         to sFileName 
92352>>>>>                Move sFieldNameArray[iCount]        to sFieldName
92353>>>>>                Move (Mid(sFieldName, 99, iLength)) to sFieldName
92354>>>>>                Move sFileName  to sRelationsArray[iCount].sFileName
92355>>>>>                Move sFieldName to sRelationsArray[iCount].sFieldName
92356>>>>>            End
92356>>>>>>
92356>>>>>        Loop
92357>>>>>>
92357>>>>>        
92357>>>>>        Function_Return sRelationsArray
92358>>>>>    End_Function  
92359>>>>>    
92359>>>>>    Function SqlUtilEnumerateLoggedInUsers String sDriverID String sDatabase Returns tSQLLoggedInUser[]
92361>>>>>        tSQLLoggedInUser[] SQLLoggedInUser
92361>>>>>        tSQLLoggedInUser[] SQLLoggedInUser
92362>>>>>        String[] sUsers sPrograms
92364>>>>>        String sSelect 
92364>>>>>        Integer iSize iCount
92364>>>>>        
92364>>>>>        Case Begin
92364>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = MSSQLDRV_ID)
92366>>>>>                Move ("SELECT RTRIM(SP.nt_username) AS Inlog, RTRIM(SP.program_name) as Programma from master.dbo.sysprocesses SP INNER JOIN master.dbo.sysdatabases SD ON SP.dbid = SD.dbid WHERE (SP.nt_username <> '') and (SP.nt_username <> 'SYSTEM') and (SD.name = '" ;                + sDatabase + "') ORDER by Inlog") to sSelect
92367>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlDAW sSelect 1 to sUsers
92368>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlDAW sSelect 2 to sPrograms
92369>>>>>                Case Break
92370>>>>>            Case (sDriverID = SQLFLEX)
92373>>>>>                Move ("SELECT RTRIM(SP.nt_username) AS Inlog, RTRIM(SP.program_name) as Programma from master.dbo.sysprocesses SP INNER JOIN master.dbo.sysdatabases SD ON SP.dbid = SD.dbid WHERE (SP.nt_username <> '') and (SP.nt_username <> 'SYSTEM') and (SD.name = '" ;                + sDatabase + "') ORDER by Inlog") to sSelect
92374>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 1 to sUsers
92375>>>>>                Get SqlEnumerateEsqlMertech sSelect 2 to sPrograms
92376>>>>>                Case Break                 
92377>>>>>            Case Else
92377>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM ("Not implemented yet for this driver (" + sDriverID + ")")
92378>>>>>>
92378>>>>>        Case End
92378>>>>>        
92378>>>>>        Move (SizeOfArray(sUsers)) to iSize
92379>>>>>        Decrement iSize
92380>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
92386>>>>>>
92386>>>>>            Move sUsers[iCount]    to SQLLoggedInUser[iCount].sUser
92387>>>>>            Move sPrograms[iCount] to SQLLoggedInUser[iCount].sProgram
92388>>>>>        Loop
92389>>>>>>
92389>>>>>        
92389>>>>>        Function_Return SQLLoggedInUser
92390>>>>>    End_Function 
