93279>>>>>        Send Delete_Data    of hoSQLHandler
93280>>>>>        Get pSQLConnection  of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to SQLConnection
93281>>>>>
93281>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
93282>>>>>        Get EnumerateDatabases of hoSQLHandler SQLConnection.sServer SQLConnection.sUserID SQLConnection.sPassword to iSize
93283>>>>>        Decrement iSize
93284>>>>>
93284>>>>>        For iCount from 0 to iSize
93290>>>>>>
