93297>>>>>    Function _SqlTableArrayDAW Returns String[]
93299>>>>>        String[] sReturnArray   
93300>>>>>        String sTable sTableType sSchema sDefSchema sComment sTableKeyWord sSysKeyWord
93300>>>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
93300>>>>>        Integer iCount iSize iItem
