93410>>>>>        Integer iItem
93410>>>>>
93410>>>>>        Get phoDB2SQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
93411>>>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
93412>>>>>
93412>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
93413>>>>>
93413>>>>>        Repeat
93413>>>>>>
93413>>>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
93414>>>>>            Move (Replaces(",", sDataSource, "")) to sDataSource
93415>>>>>            Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
93416>>>>>            Increment iItem
93417>>>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
93419>>>>>
