93422>>>>>    Function _SqlDatabasesArrayODBC Returns String[]
93424>>>>>        String[] sReturnArray
93425>>>>>        String sDataSource
93425>>>>>        Handle hoSQLHandler
93425>>>>>        Integer iItem
93425>>>>>
93425>>>>>        Get phoODBCSQLHandler to hoSQLHandler
93426>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id CLIERR_LOGIN_UNSUCCESSFUL
93427>>>>>
93427>>>>>        Send SeedDataSources of hoSQLHandler
93428>>>>>
93428>>>>>        Repeat
93428>>>>>>
93428>>>>>            Get DataSources of hoSQLHandler to sDataSource
93429>>>>>            If (Trim(sDataSource) <> "" and not(sDataSource contains "*.")) Begin
93431>>>>>                Move (Trim(sDataSource)) to sReturnArray[iItem]
93432>>>>>                Increment iItem
93433>>>>>            End
93433>>>>>>
93433>>>>>        Until (sDataSource = "")
