96989>>>>>    // Helper function. Takes a DF_FILE_XXXX_NAME value as parameter and 
96989>>>>>    // returns the table name only; stripped of any path or filename extension.
96989>>>>>    Function _TableNameOnly String sName Returns String
96991>>>>>        String sPath sExt
96991>>>>>        
96991>>>>>        Get ParseFolderName sName to sPath
96992>>>>>        If (sPath <> "") Begin
96994>>>>>            Move (Replace(sPath, sName, "")) to sName
96995>>>>>        End                                                  
96995>>>>>>
96995>>>>>        Get ParseFileExtension sName to sExt
96996>>>>>        If (sExt <> "") Begin
96998>>>>>            Move (Replace(("." + sExt), sName, "")) to sName
96999>>>>>        End
96999>>>>>>
96999>>>>>        
96999>>>>>        Function_Return sName
97000>>>>>    End_Function
