97458>>>>>    Function psDriverID Returns String
97460>>>>>        String sDriverID
97460>>>>>        
97460>>>>>        Send Ignore_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_BAD_MESSAGE
97461>>>>>        // This should get it from the parent object (when using the cDbUpdateHandler class)
97461>>>>>        Delegate Get psDriverID to sDriverID
97463>>>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_BAD_MESSAGE
97464>>>>>        Move False to Err
97465>>>>>
97465>>>>>        // ...and in case it didn't use property of this class. Then the library is
97465>>>>>        // probably used as "utilites" from a special made program and
97465>>>>>        // the ghoSQLConnectionHandler must have been setup
97465>>>>>        If (sDriverID = "") Begin
97467>>>>>            Get psDriverID of ghoSQLConnectionHandler to sDriverID
97468>>>>>        End            
97468>>>>>>
