97482>>>>>        Set Error_Report_Mode to DUF_ERROR_NO_REPORT
97483>>>>>        Delegate Get piDbType to iRetval
97485>>>>>        Set Error_Report_Mode to DUF_ERROR_REPORT
97486>>>>>        Send Trap_Error of Error_Object_Id DFERR_BAD_MESSAGE
97487>>>>>
