97949>>>>>// Provides support for db aware scrolling containers.
97949>>>>>// Scrolling containers is provided by creating two objects,
97949>>>>>// a host (dbScrollingContainer) and a scrolling clientarea (dbScrollingClientArea)
97949>>>>>// The host has no public interface, you just drop the object. It should have only one child object
97949>>>>>// and that should be a scrolling client-area. If it is not, it is an error. It is also considered
97949>>>>>// an error to place a scrolling client area in any object other than a scrolling container.
97949>>>>>
97949>>>>>Use DFClient.pkg
97949>>>>>Use cScrollingContainerMixin.pkg
Including file: cScrollingContainerMixin.pkg    (E:\DataFlex 19.0\Pkg\cScrollingContainerMixin.pkg)
97949>>>>>>>// Mixin classes for scrolling container support:
97949>>>>>>>// cScrollingContainerMixin & cScrollingClientAreaMixin
97949>>>>>>>// These are used by cSrollingContainer / cScrollingClientArea and
97949>>>>>>>// dbScrollingContainer / dbScrollingClientArea.
97949>>>>>>>// The scrolling container has no public interface, you just drop the object. It should have only one child object
97949>>>>>>>// and that should be a scrolling client-area. If it is not, it is an error. It is also considered
97949>>>>>>>// an error to place a scrolling client area in any object other than a scrolling container.
