98098>>>>>>>            Move 0 to ScrollInfo.nPos
98099>>>>>>>            Move (SetScrollInfo (hWnd, If(bVert,SB_VERT,SB_HORZ), AddressOf (ScrollInfo), True)) to iVoid
98100>>>>>>>
