98406>>>>>>>    Procedure Define_cScrollingContainerMixin
98408>>>>>>>        Forward Set Border_Style to Border_None
98410>>>>>>>        Set pbSizeToClientArea to False // scrollbars and clientsize do not mix
98411>>>>>>>        Forward Set peAnchors to anAll
98413>>>>>>>
98413>>>>>>>        // forcing scrollbars right away seems to make painting better
98413>>>>>>>        Set Window_Style WS_HSCROLL to True
98414>>>>>>>        Set Window_Style WS_VSCROLL to True
98415>>>>>>>
98415>>>>>>>        Property Handle phoScrollingClientArea 0
98416>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
