98467>>>>>>>        Handle hoClient
98467>>>>>>>        Forward Send End_Construct_Object
98469>>>>>>>        Get phoScrollingClientArea to hoClient
98470>>>>>>>        If (hoClient) Begin
98472>>>>>>>            Send AutoSetTabWorkspaceView of hoClient
98473>>>>>>>        End
98473>>>>>>>>
98473>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
98474>>>>>>>
98474>>>>>>>End_Class
