100627>>>Function MakeSQLDatabaseBackup Returns Boolean
100630>>>    Handle ho
100630>>>    Boolean bOK bDefault
100630>>>    String sDatabase sPath sBackupName 
100630>>>    
100630>>>    Move (oSQLDatabaseBackup_dg(Self)) to ho
100631>>>    Set pbOK of ho to False
100632>>>    Send Popup of ho   
100633>>>    
100633>>>    Get pbOk of ho to bOK
100634>>>    If (bOK = True) Begin        
100636>>>        Get Value of (oDatabase_fm(ho))   to sDatabase
100637>>>        Get Value of (oBackupName_fm(ho)) to sBackupName
100638>>>        Get Checked_State of (oUseDefaultBackupFolder_cb(ho)) to bDefault
100639>>>        If (bDefault = False) Begin
100641>>>            Get Value of (oPath_fm(ho)) to sPath
100642>>>        End
100642>>>>
100642>>>        Get SqlUtilBackupDatabaseToDisk of ghoDbUpdateFunctionLibrary sDatabase sBackupName sPath True to bOK
100643>>>    End
100643>>>>
100643>>>    
100643>>>    Function_Return bOK
100644>>>End_Function
